"5f6c8a3eef1f7a04a164b95e3281637e03e58aee","tid":2291642,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荒謬判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉<span class=\"gold\">伸腳絆倒</span>警員 前公務員襲警罪成判<span class=\"gold\">囚兩月</span> 官：以儆效尤、防範未然<br />\n<br />\n涉向便衣警<span class=\"gold\">背脊貼文宣</span> 地產經紀襲警罪成<span class=\"gold\">囚 3 周</span> 官：行為極具羞辱成份<br />\n<br />\n中大內地生畢業禮涉<span class=\"gold\">持刀</span>唱國歌 獲撤控准簽保守行為 官質疑：嚴重過雷射筆<br />\n<br />\n【11.11 三罷】教師被控襲警罪成 一度遭還押小欖 判<span class=\"gold\">囚 9 周</span>准保釋候上訴 官斥未見悔意<br />\n<br />\n陳志全私人檢控郭偉強 律政司<span class=\"gold\">要求介入</span> <span class=\"gold\">不提證供起訴</span><br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨麥當勞打人案 施襲男子被<span class=\"gold\">判社服令</span><br />\n打人+刑事毁壞唔洗坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【旺角 10.6 】內地客、清路障男子遭「私了」 清潔工判囚 4 年 另兩被告各囚 15 個月<br />\n第二被告開遮 推咗一下 坐15個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n地盤工暴動襲痱滋警罪成<span class=\"gold\">囚4年</span> 官：判刑不考慮政治 對再判品格良好青年入獄感無奈<br />\n圍狗總案 事發歷時15秒 好似都係打咗幾鎚踢幾腳 咁就4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同下面斬人睇齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連儂隧道斬人導遊求情：不幸事因社運 <span class=\"gold\">官讚情操高尚</span> <span class=\"gold\">同情減刑</span>囚 45 月 狂轟示威者<br />\n拎把刀落街明顯有預謀 斬到人入icu都係坐得嗰4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n涉亮𠝹刀疑襲警遭女警槍擊 無業漢被控轉介區院再訊<br />\n𠝹刀就開槍 唔講以為俾西瓜刀劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />荒謬判刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n節錄唔曬靠巴絲幫我加上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ac13121503895d10672c17f7bda8796d3cda78","tid":2291642,"uid":321296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17572fc46b7419d144b80b54df18154416737496","tid":2291642,"uid":275498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">律政司一句 就叫你老母粒高院皮啦 </span></strong>"},{"pid":"c99ce6edd318d286ff165ff06ad1b0d68e417468","tid":2291642,"uid":55317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"支支人大準備釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea7f0c2a6dd9710014845cab69a26c2ff8994bb","tid":2291642,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:06:10.000Z","msg":"good cop bad cop"},{"pid":"edb9f5e5b4ef3b29bbe1e39d240c3ae74e6d2dd6","tid":2291642,"uid":52760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:09:03.000Z","msg":"到家仲相信香港有法治既<br />\n果堆人都ON99"},{"pid":"48aa2f36412cc7ade96c17856db5b45e55ae8100","tid":2291642,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"違反人權法有咩後果"